Titolo: Donkey Kong 3

Anno: 1983

Descrizione: Donkey Kong 3 is the third video game in the Donkey Kong series by Nintendo. It was released for arcades worldwide in 1983 and the Family Computer in 1984, then later released in North America for the Nintendo Entertainment System in 1986. The gameplay departs from previous Donkey Kong games, being primarily a shooter game, and starring an exterminator named Stanley instead of Mario.It was re-released on the Wii Virtual Console in North America on July 14, 2008, and in Europe on January 9, 2009.

